@host = http://localhost:5111

### Create team member (do this before assigning tasks)
POST {{host}}/api/team-members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Taylor Kim",
  "email": "taylor@example.com"
}

### List team members
GET {{host}}/api/team-members

### List work items
GET {{host}}/api/work-items

### Search title + filter status
GET {{host}}/api/work-items?q=draft&status=InProgress

### Get by id
GET {{host}}/api/work-items/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222201

### Create
POST {{host}}/api/work-items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Smoke test task",
  "description": null,
  "status": null,
  "priority": null,
  "assigneeId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111101",
  "assignerId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111102"
}

### Delete (replace id after create)
DELETE {{host}}/api/work-items/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
